{
  "id": "69c471fb05d0ca5f42a00c34",
  "title": "staの朝ルーティン",
  "created": 1774481917,
  "updated": 1774482155,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c471fb05d0ca5f42a00c34",
      "text": "staの朝ルーティン",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774481917,
      "updated": 1774481917
    },
    {
      "id": "69c471fc00000000008ecfc2",
      "text": "\t起きる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774481917,
      "updated": 1774481919
    },
    {
      "id": "69c472d300000000008ecfcc",
      "text": "\t\t今は4:30～4:40くらい[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774482132,
      "updated": 1774482141
    },
    {
      "id": "69c471fe00000000008ecfc4",
      "text": "\tT-falで湯を沸かす → トイレ → 口の中ゆすいで洗顔",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774481919,
      "updated": 1774481983
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4721c00000000008ecfc5",
      "text": "\t沸かした湯でドリップコーヒー入れつつ、お茶を水筒に入れて一口飲む",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774481949,
      "updated": 1774481989
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4724400000000008ecfc6",
      "text": "\tデスクについてコーヒー + [BASE BREAD]2個で朝食がてらネットや作業",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774481989,
      "updated": 1774482120
    },
    {
      "id": "69c472c700000000008ecfcb",
      "text": "\t\t[2026/03/25#69c2f14f00000000003e0000]はここが落ち着いたときに書いてるね（5:17）[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774482121,
      "updated": 1774482155
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4725b00000000008ecfc7",
      "text": "\tリモートで出社",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774482012,
      "updated": 1774482016
    },
    {
      "id": "69c472e100000000008ecfcd",
      "text": "\t\t大体6:00くらい[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774482147,
      "updated": 1774482153
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4726a00000000008ecfc8",
      "text": "\tその日のコンテキスト全部頭に入れて検討出来る状態つくった後、散歩",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774482027,
      "updated": 1774482042
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4727800000000008ecfc9",
      "text": "\t散歩帰宅後、検討結果を反映していく",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774482042,
      "updated": 1774482057
    },
    {
      "id": "69c4728c00000000008ecfca",
      "text": "\tゴリゴリしてたら 8:30（会社の標準的な出社時間）が来て賑やかになってくる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774482061,
      "updated": 1774482081
    },
    {
      "id": "69c471fe00000000008ecfc3",
